---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/service-detail.css';
---

<Layout
  title="Webサイト・アプリ構築 | ししゃも｜吉川昌宏"
  description="7年のWeb開発経験を活かし、要件定義から実装まで対応。シンプルなサイトから業務システムまで。"
  currentPage="services"
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="パンくずリスト">
    <a href="/">ホーム</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
    <a href="/services/">サービス</a>
    <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
    <span aria-current="page">Webサイト・アプリ構築</span>
  </nav>

  <!-- Service Hero -->
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="service-hero-blob"></div>
    <div class="service-hero-inner">
      <div class="service-hero-icon">💻</div>
      <h1>Webサイト・アプリ構築</h1>
      <p>7年のWeb開発経験を活かし、要件定義から実装まで対応。シンプルなサイトから業務システムまで。</p>
      <div class="service-hero-price">
        <span class="amount">50〜200</span>
        <span class="unit">万円/PJ</span>
      </div>
      <div class="service-hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary">無料相談する →</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn-secondary">← サービス一覧</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Content -->
  <div class="service-content">
    <div class="service-content-inner">
      <!-- Problems -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>😥 こんな課題ありませんか？</h2>
        <div class="problem-list">
          <div class="problem-item">
            <p>会社のホームページが古くなり、スマホ対応もできていない</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-item">
            <p>Excelで管理している業務をシステム化したいが、何から始めれば...</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-item">
            <p>制作会社に依頼したいが、要望をうまく伝えられる自信がない</p>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-item">
            <p>既存システムの改修を頼みたいが、元の開発会社と連絡が取れない</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Features -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>✨ サービスの特徴</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
            <h3>コーポレートサイト制作</h3>
            <p>会社の顔となるWebサイトを制作。スマホ対応、SEO対策、更新のしやすさを考慮した設計で、集客に貢献します。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">⚙️</div>
            <h3>業務用Webアプリ開発</h3>
            <p>顧客管理、在庫管理、予約システムなど、御社の業務に合わせたWebアプリケーションを開発します。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔧</div>
            <h3>既存システム改修</h3>
            <p>使いづらくなったシステムの改修、機能追加、セキュリティ対応など。他社が作ったシステムも対応可能です。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3>要件定義からお任せ</h3>
            <p>「何を作りたいか」を一緒に整理するところから支援。技術がわからなくても大丈夫です。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Flow -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>📋 開発の流れ</h2>
        <div class="flow-list">
          <div class="flow-item" data-step="1">
            <h3>ヒアリング・要件定義</h3>
            <p>御社の課題と実現したいことをヒアリング。必要な機能を整理し、開発範囲を明確にします。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-item" data-step="2">
            <h3>設計・見積り</h3>
            <p>画面構成や機能仕様を設計し、開発スケジュールと費用をお見積りします。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-item" data-step="3">
            <h3>開発・テスト</h3>
            <p>設計に基づき開発を進め、随時進捗を共有。テストを重ね、品質を確保します。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-item" data-step="4">
            <h3>納品・運用サポート</h3>
            <p>本番環境へのリリースと操作説明。納品後の保守・改修もご相談ください。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Pricing -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>💰 料金の目安</h2>
        <div class="pricing-cards">
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <div class="pricing-plan">コーポレートサイト</div>
            <div class="pricing-amount">50</div>
            <div class="pricing-unit">万円〜</div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">5〜10ページ程度の会社紹介サイト。スマホ対応、お問い合わせフォーム付き。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card popular">
            <div class="pricing-plan">業務アプリ（小規模）</div>
            <div class="pricing-amount">100</div>
            <div class="pricing-unit">万円〜</div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">顧客管理や予約管理など、単機能の業務システム。クラウド対応。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <div class="pricing-plan">業務アプリ（中規模）</div>
            <div class="pricing-amount">200</div>
            <div class="pricing-unit">万円〜</div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">複数機能を連携した業務システム。既存システムとの連携も対応。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Services -->
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>🔗 関連サービス</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/services/dx-consulting/" class="related-card">
            <div class="related-card-icon">🚀</div>
            <h3>DX推進サポート</h3>
            <p>システム導入の前段階から、業務プロセス改善を含めて支援します。</p>
            <span class="related-link">詳しく見る →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/services/it-strategy/" class="related-card">
            <div class="related-card-icon">📋</div>
            <h3>IT戦略策定</h3>
            <p>開発の優先順位や投資計画を、経営視点で整理します。</p>
            <span class="related-link">詳しく見る →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/services/#ai" class="related-card">
            <div class="related-card-icon">🤖</div>
            <h3>AIツール開発</h3>
            <p>生成AIを活用した業務自動化ツールの開発も対応可能です。</p>
            <span class="related-link">詳しく見る →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="service-cta">
    <h2>まずは無料相談から</h2>
    <p>作りたいものが明確でなくても大丈夫です。<br>課題をお聞かせください。一緒に整理しましょう。</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary">無料相談する →</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Breadcrumb */
  .breadcrumb {
    padding: 5.5rem 2rem 1rem; background: var(--gray-lighter); font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--gray); transition: color 0.3s; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
  .breadcrumb span { color: var(--gray); margin: 0 0.5rem; }

  /* Service Hero */
  .service-hero {
    padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light), #EFF6FF, #DBEAFE);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .service-hero::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; right: -30%; width: 80%; height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(37,99,235,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .service-hero-blob {
    position: absolute; right: 10%; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 350px; height: 350px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
    opacity: 0.08; animation: morph 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .service-hero-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
  .service-hero-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .service-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), var(--primary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
  }
  .service-hero-inner > p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray); max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .service-hero-price {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.375rem;
    background: var(--white); padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-hero-price .amount {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: #3b82f6;
  }
  .service-hero-price .unit { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray); }
  .service-hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* Service Content */
  .service-content { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
  .service-content-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .content-section { margin-bottom: 5rem; }
  .content-section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .content-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .content-section h2::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gray-light), transparent);
  }

  /* Problem List */
  .problem-list {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .problem-item {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-light); transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .problem-item::before { content: '😰'; font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .problem-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, white, #EFF6FF);
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }
  .problem-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Feature Grid */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .feature-card {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;
    border: 2px solid transparent; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transition: all 0.4s;
  }
  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl), var(--shadow-glow);
  }
  .feature-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .feature-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Flow List */
  .flow-list { position: relative; padding-left: 3rem; }
  .flow-list::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 20px; bottom: 20px; width: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), var(--accent), var(--secondary)); border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .flow-item {
    position: relative; padding: 2rem; padding-left: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); border: 2px solid var(--gray-light); transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .flow-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .flow-item:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateX(5px); }
  .flow-item::before {
    content: attr(data-step); position: absolute; left: -3rem; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(-50%);
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--light);
  }
  .flow-item h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .flow-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Pricing Cards */
  .pricing-cards {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-light); transition: all 0.3s; text-align: center;
  }
  .pricing-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }
  .pricing-card.popular {
    border-color: var(--primary); position: relative;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), var(--shadow-glow);
  }
  .pricing-card.popular::before {
    content: 'おすすめ'; position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    color: white; padding: 0.25rem 1rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .pricing-plan { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pricing-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: #3b82f6;
  }
  .pricing-unit { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray); }
  .pricing-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Related Grid */
  .related-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .related-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-lighter), white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 1.5rem; transition: all 0.3s;
    border: 2px solid transparent; display: block;
  }
  .related-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .related-card-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .related-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .related-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .related-link { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem; }

  /* Service CTA */
  .service-cta {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark), #1E40AF);
    text-align: center; color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .service-cta::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; right: -30%; width: 80%; height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .service-cta > * { position: relative; }
  .service-cta h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-cta p { opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .service-cta .btn-primary { background: var(--white); color: var(--primary); }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .breadcrumb { padding: 5rem 1.5rem 0.75rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .service-hero { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .service-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .service-hero-inner > p { font-size: 1rem; }
    .service-hero-icon { font-size: 3rem; }
    .service-hero-price { padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; }
    .service-hero-price .amount { font-size: 2rem; }
    .service-hero-cta { flex-direction: column; }

    .service-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .content-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .content-section h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; }

    .problem-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feature-card { padding: 1.5rem; }

    .flow-list { padding-left: 2rem; }
    .flow-item { padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
    .flow-item::before { left: -2rem; width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 0.85rem; }

    .pricing-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pricing-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .pricing-amount { font-size: 2rem; }

    .related-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .service-cta { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .service-cta h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .breadcrumb { padding: 4.5rem 1rem 0.5rem; }
    .service-hero { padding: 1.5rem 1rem 2.5rem; }
    .service-hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .service-content { padding: 2.5rem 1rem; }
    .flow-list { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    .flow-item::before { left: -1.5rem; width: 28px; height: 28px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  }

  @media (hover: none) {
    .problem-item:hover, .feature-card:hover, .flow-item:hover,
    .pricing-card:hover, .related-card:hover { transform: none; }
  }

  /* Dark mode */
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .service-hero-price .amount {
    color: #60a5fa;
  }
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .pricing-amount {
    color: #60a5fa;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    html:not([data-theme="light"]) .service-hero-price .amount {
      color: #60a5fa;
    }
    html:not([data-theme="light"]) .pricing-amount {
      color: #60a5fa;
    }
  }
</style>
